  "text": "The tradeoffs. Since it requires an extra memory buffer to store δ t , T2 is not free: however, this increase in memory is small relative to the cost of storing the entire history of w. Figure 4 shows that combining T1+T2 enables fine-grained pipeline parallelism to converge with ResNet50 on CIFAR10 when T1 alone cannot, which justifies the benefits in statistical performance brought by its 25%-33% weight and optimizer memory increase. [CITATION_1] ",
